title: Documentary on art of modern politics to screen on campus (York University)
text: ( Source : York University ) A documentary film that puts the lens on the art of politics in the 21st century will screen at York University's Price Family Cinema on Oct. 14 at 6 p.m. Punching for Power: Politics as Showmanship is a free event
